&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a commercially driven Channel Development Executive who knows how to build, scale, and activate a partner ecosystem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This role combines hunting for new strategic partners with structuring and growing an existing network across EMEA. You’ll work with distributors, resellers, and system integrators to create a high-performing, revenue-generating partner channel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If you’re someone who combines sales drive with structure, and enjoys turning partnerships into real business impact—this is your role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Identify, attract, and onboard new partners across EMEA (distributors, resellers, system integrators)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build and manage a portfolio of partners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develop and execute partner business plans focused on revenue growth and pipeline generation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Enable partners through training, positioning, and joint go-to-market activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Drive co-selling motions and support partners in closing deals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Bring structure to the partner ecosystem: segmentation, performance tracking, and optimization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Monitor and grow partner-driven revenue and pipeline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Act as the key link between partners and internal teams (sales, marketing, product)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A highly commercial profile with a strong focus on revenue and results&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;3–5 years of experience in sales, ideally starting in direct sales and evolving into a partner/channel role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, a

&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Summary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a passionate compiler engineer with a strong interest in software security to join our team working on iXGuard. Our LLVM-based software protection product focuses on hardening iOS applications against both static analysis and dynamic tampering.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate loves to come up with new ideas for our next code hardening layer to counter reverse engineering techniques and runtime hooking. You make good use of the available flexibility in our team to test those ideas and experiment further. The person we are looking to hire is able to prioritize tasks and constantly tries to improve our codebase. He or she is a disciplined and independent worker who takes pride in his or her work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Maintain and improve our existing code base.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Research, test and implement additional code hardening techniques.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Support customers in the usage of our software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Continuously improve the code quality through extensive testing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Stay up-to-date with reverse engineering practices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Profile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Master&#39;s degree in Computer Science.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Ideally 2 to 3 years of experience in a similar role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent modern C++ skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Previous experience working with complex code bases.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with LLVM tools and libraries.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience with compiler internals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;f

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Are you enthusiastic about empowering and supporting developers in creating the next generation of mobile apps?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Guardsquare is looking for a developer or technically savvy person who is passionate about mobile app security and engaging with peers both digitally and in person to understand their challenges and champion solutions for their needs. As part of the marketing team, your role will be to engage with the developer community through forums, speaking at conferences and events, creating relevant content, and more to help developers achieve the ideal mix of speed to market, performance, user experience and security for mobile apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Content creation: proposing ideas for and writing compelling blogs, creating tutorials and how-tos, video demos and social media and community posts diving into code and / or the architecture of mobile apps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Public engagement: serving as a panelist or presenting at conferences, meetups, relevant industry events on behalf of Guardsquare&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Community engagement: actively participating in developer forums, social media groups and online communities through answering questions and generating relevant discussions related to mobile app security&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Influencer engagement: building relationships and identifying opportunities for collaboration with key influencers and thought leaders on behalf of Guardsquare&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Mobile app security advocate: communicating the value of Guardsquare’s products, ensuring the developer community is aware of new offerings, capabilities and beta initiatives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Social media management: Ensuring Guardsquare’s social media presence is relevant and the content is compelling for developers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Feedback: Gather and share product feedback with marketing and product teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-s

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’ve ever built your own PC, run a home lab, broken something just to figure out how it works, or spent hours tuning a setup until it’s just right, you’ll probably feel at home here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a mid-level IT System Administrator who brings a solid foundation and is eager to keep learning and growing. You should be comfortable getting up to speed quickly, contributing early, and taking on more ownership over time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role sits between helpdesk and systems: part hands-on support, part infrastructure. You’ll work across a global environment covering Unix/Linux systems, networking, cloud infrastructure, and multi-OS endpoints, with a particular opportunity to strengthen our Windows capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How your time is split: roughly 60% infrastructure and automation, 30% hands-on employee support and onboarding, and 10% security and compliance work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on role with real ownership: not ticket-only support, and not a pure architecture role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires being in the Leuven office 4 days per week, with the potential for more flexibility as the team grows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Candidates must be legally authorized to work in Belgium at the time of application. Please note that we are unable to provide visa or work permit sponsorship for this role.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure &amp;amp; Automation (60%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and improve our on-premise and cloud infrastructure (Proxmox virtualization on Dell servers, Google Cloud Platform, networking)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer systems and services across Linux/Unix and Windows environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy, monitor, and troubleshoot containerized services and build environments using Docker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and maintain Python scripts and use tools like Ansible to automate provisioning, configuration, and repetitive tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor system performance and network health (TCP/IP, DNS, DHCP), resolving issues to minimize downtime&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track IT assets, hardware inventory, and software licenses, and keep technical documentation accurate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support &amp;amp; Onboarding (30%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a hands-on IT point of contact for a global team, providing on-site and remote support across macOS, Linux, Windows, and mobile devices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute onboarding and offboarding (accounts, devices, access), with the goal of continuously improving and automating workflows through MDM tooling (Mosyle, Intune, NinjaOne)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage configurations and integrations for collaboration tools such as Google Workspace, Slack, GitHub, and Atlassian&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a dependable go-to for day-to-day technical issues and employee support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security &amp;amp; Compliance (10%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and test backups, disaster recovery, and business continuity procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement security measures including access controls, patch management, and event logging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support IAM practices, vulnerability remediation, audits, incident response, and access reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Environment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloud:&lt;/strong&gt; Google Cloud Platform&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On-prem:&lt;/strong&gt; Proxmox on Dell servers&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Endpoints:&lt;/strong&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Guardsquare is looking for Team Leads to join us in our Leuven office and lead one of our Leuven based iXGuard (C++/LLVM) or DexGuard (Java) teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In this role you will be responsible for a team of about 5 to 7 software engineers working within an agile software development environment. The ideal candidate started their career technically and has a good understanding of software engineering within a high-tech start/scale-up, and grew into or is now ready for a team lead role.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your key responsibilities will be:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Own the results delivered by your team. You lead day-to-day development; assign tasks, track progress, ensure timely delivery and high quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Mentor engineers, foster collaboration, and motivate the team to reach company and personal objectives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Set coding standards and best practices for maintainable solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work with product teams to translate business needs into technical specifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Implement and enforce testing practices to deliver reliable software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Encourage new ideas and own engineering processes to drive continuous improvement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Represent Guardsquare’s R&amp;amp;D values, its products and its culture.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Masters in computer science with 5+ years of experience, of which at least 3 as a Team Lead&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Proven track record of achieving results with teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, ar

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a high-energy, driven professional, with natural sales instincts to join our growing organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be tasked with opening doors and proactively building interest at potential clients, and being a key member of the sales team in Leuven.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guardsquare offers a focused, driven, and independent environment where you will be challenged to grow, asked to contribute, and mentored into building a stronger sales skillset. This will open the door to growing into a closing role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with your sales and marketing colleagues;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate leads that might be interested in a collaboration;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively target prospects via e-mailing and outbound calling;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make amazing first impressions and help schedule meetings;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain active engagement with prospects and clients through follow-up;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage account administration and offers;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grow as a sales person and take on bigger and greater challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor or master in a relevant field (Business, communication, IT...);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a young graduate or have a first working experience in sales in a relevant field;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding verbal and written communication in Spanish, Portuguese and English. Knowledge of any other languages will be a plus.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good knowledge of MS Office;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize and self manage time and tasks;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to take initiative and build your own success;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A positive and can-do attitude.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Big interest in Sales and Mobile Security;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a rapidly expanding and changing environment;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for our products and sales;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The desire to learn and grow with the company.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Guardsquare offers you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A full time job with a competitive salary package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are provided with the tools &amp;amp; flexibility to develop yourself successfully&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An international environment where you will interact with motivated &amp;amp; open colleagues with different backgrounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A workplace where you can share and implement your ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A hybrid work policy, which helps guarantee an excellent work-life balance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Guardsquare, we take pride in being a diverse and multicultural company with team members representing numerous nationalities. We value different perspectives and opinions throughout the business which has contributed to our being &lt;strong&gt;the market leader in mobile application security.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of a &lt;strong&gt;dynamic &lt;/strong&gt;team that strives for excellence and focuses on continuous education and enhancement in skills. We &lt;strong&gt;encourage &amp;amp; empower&lt;/strong&gt; our &lt;strong&gt;trusted colleague&lt;/strong&gt;s to share their opinions, actively collaborate, and continue to learn and grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So, what are you waiting for? Join us!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You can apply for this opportunity by filling out the application form below!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
